The utilities package for the URLyBird Application.

    UrlyBirdApplicationConstants
    This class holds the constants, not unique to the GUI classes, used in the URLyBird Application.

    Holds the constants for the GUI classes.

Package suncertify.utilities Description

The utilities package for the URLyBird Application. This package holds the constants and other misc. resources used in the application.
